EndeavourOS i3wm Keybindings cheat sheet:

--> to update this run the following command:
wget --backups=1 https://raw.githubusercontent.com/endeavouros-team/endeavouros-i3wm-setup/main/.config/i3/keybindings -P ~/.config/i3/

All sources and updates are available at GitHub:
https://github.com/endeavouros-team/endeavouros-i3wm-setup

For reference consult our WIKI:
https://discovery.endeavouros.com/window-tiling-managers/i3-wm/

ď…Ľ = windows key

# # start xfce4-terminal
# ď…Ľ+Return 

# kill focused window
ď…Ľ+q

# Application menu search by typing (fancy Rofi menu):
ď…Ľ+d

# Window switcher menu (fancy Rofi menu):
ď…Ľ+t

# fancy exit-menu on bottom right:
ď…Ľ+Shift+e

# Lock the system
# lock with a picture or blurring the screen (options in config)
ď…Ľ+l

# reload the configuration file
ď…Ľ+Shift+c

# restart i3 inplace (preserves your layout/session, can be used to upgrade i3)
ď…Ľ+Shift+r

# keybinding in fancy rofi (automated)
F1

# full keybinding list in editor:
ď…Ľ+F1

# change window focus
ď…Ľ+j focus left
ď…Ľ+k focus down
ď…Ľ+b focus up
ď…Ľ+o focus right

# alternatively, you can use the cursor keys:
ď…Ľ+Left focus left
ď…Ľ+Down focus down
ď…Ľ+Up focus up
ď…Ľ+Right focus right

# move a focused window
ď…Ľ+Shift+j move left
ď…Ľ+Shift+k move down
ď…Ľ+Shift+b move up
ď…Ľ+Shift+o move right

# alternatively, you can use the cursor keys:
ď…Ľ+Shift+Left move left
ď…Ľ+Shift+Down move down
ď…Ľ+Shift+Up move up
ď…Ľ+Shift+Right move right

# split in horizontal orientation
ď…Ľ+h split h

# split in vertical orientation
ď…Ľ+v split v

# enter fullscreen mode for the focused container
ď…Ľ+f fullscreen toggle

# change container layout (stacked, tabbed, toggle split)
ď…Ľ+s layout stacking
ď…Ľ+g layout tabbed
ď…Ľ+e layout toggle split

# toggle tiling / floating
ď…Ľ+Shift+space floating toggle

# change focus between tiling / floating windows
ď…Ľ+space focus mode_toggle

# focus the parent container
ď…Ľ+a focus parent

# focus the child container
#ď…Ľ+d focus child

# resize floating window
ď…Ľ+right mouse button

